<paragraph id="8BD0502BFFE5FFE9838B4E862E023B53" blockId="1.[136,1453,704,942]" pageId="1" pageNumber="249">
<taxonomicName id="4C6F2BA8FFE5FFE9838B4E862EB03AC7" authorityName="Trovo. A. Habit" authorityYear="2021" box="[136,387,704,725]" class="Liliopsida" family="Eriocaulaceae" genus="Paepalanthus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="1" pageNumber="249" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="mellosilvae">
<emphasis id="B91B8C39FFE5FFE9838B4E862EB03AC7" box="[136,387,704,725]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="249">Paepalanthus mellosilvae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
differs from 
<taxonomicName id="4C6F2BA8FFE5FFE981134E862CF03AC4" authority="Ruhland (1903: 216)" authorityName="Ruhland" authorityPageNumber="216" authorityYear="1903" box="[528,963,704,726]" class="Liliopsida" family="Eriocaulaceae" genus="Paepalanthus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="1" pageNumber="249" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="harmsii">
<emphasis id="B91B8C39FFE5FFE981134E862DD43AC7" box="[528,743,704,725]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="249">Paepalanthus harmsii</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFFE2DDAFFE5FFE981F14E862CF03AC4" author="Ruhland, W." box="[754,963,704,726]" pageId="1" pageNumber="249" refId="ref3050" refString="Ruhland, W. (1903) Eriocaulaceae. In: Engler, A. (Ed.) Das Pflanzenreich. Regni vegetabilis conspectus 4 heft 30. Wilhelm Engelmann, Leipzig, 294 pp." type="book" year="1903">Ruhland (1903: 216)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
by the presence of a rhizome, narrower leaves, more numerous scapes, narrower capitula, sparsely pilose involucral bracts, and obdeltate floral bracts. The pilosity of the floral parts are also rather different, being usually more densely pilose on the abaxial surface and margins of the petals and sepals of 
<taxonomicName id="4C6F2BA8FFE5FFE986994F4E2E193B53" authorityName="Trovo. A. Habit" authorityYear="2021" class="Liliopsida" family="Eriocaulaceae" genus="Paepalanthus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="1" pageNumber="249" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="mellosilvae">
<emphasis id="B91B8C39FFE5FFE986994F4E2E193B53" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="249">P. mellosilvae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
